          chance with a simple call.</p>
          <p align="center"><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/getinfo" role="button" align="center">Get Going &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <!-- Example row of columns -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2 align="center">Trusted</h2>
            <p align=center>The most trusted app in America. Using state of the art technology, allows the user to quickly pay
            for the service without any worries. Backed by countless(0) companies.</p>
            <p align="center"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_companies_of_the_United_States" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
