            <p align="center">Easy to use. Easy to manage. Simply provide what message you want and what time you want the
              message to be sent to you phone and everything is set for you. No time wasted signing up. </p>
            <p align="center"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/17180/windows-10-make-your-pc-easier-to-use" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
