            <blockquote>
              "The greatest invention of our time!" -The New Yurk Times
              "Changes the way people see the world" -Tim Magazine
            </blockquote>
            <p align="center"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.nytimes.com/" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

      </div> <!-- /container -->

